Interface IPhantomProcessConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    de.flapdoodle.embed.process.config.IExecutableProcessConfig

    public interface IPhantomProcessConfig
extends de.flapdoodle.embed.process.config.IExecutableProcessConfig
    Provides command line arguments for the Phantom process itself. Individual properties aren't documented to avoid duplication. See Command Line Interface for details on each property.
    See Also:
    IPhantomCommandFormatter
